sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of Home Depot (HD) topped the list of the day's best performing components of the S&P 500 index, trading up 4.0%.
Year to date, Home Depot registers a 25.9% gain.
And the worst performing S&P 500 component thus far on the day is Conagra Brands (CAG), trading down 4.4%.
Conagra Brands is showing a gain of 34.4% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are TJX Companies (TJX), trading down 4.0%, and Medtronic (MDT), trading up 3.7% on the day.
